  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3352970/extras/ca8e676c3236e76fd6a96755207de135.avif?t=1738853871\" width=367 height=79 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3352970/extras/5da9508ba938974577d5e1a8a0a11b66.avif?t=1738853871\" width=648 height=246 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight to escape from the dimensional prison: choose one of the six warriors </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and prepare for battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3352970/extras/28ad32ade2bdc1cca734bd1b334030af.avif?t=1738853871\" width=367 height=79 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Anima, the enigmatic Dungeon Mistress, rules with cunning and power. In her dark domain, six slaves fight under her command, facing brutal and challenging trials. However, the battles are not only physical; Anima designs these confrontations to forge indomitable warriors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3352970/extras/6aa98c3b917d6d2da2654af63d5cfddd.avif?t=1738853871\" width=367 height=79 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Currently, the game includes:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 7 playable characters</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 6 stages</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Story mode for all 8 characters</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 7 original music themes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Vs. AI mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Training mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Arcade Stick arcade support</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- A controller is required for local multiplayer.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Full Compatible.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3352970/extras/ca8e676c3236e76fd6a96755207de135.avif?t=1738853871\" width=367 height=79 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3352970/extras/5da9508ba938974577d5e1a8a0a11b66.avif?t=1738853871\" width=648 height=246 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight to escape from the dimensional prison: choose one of the six warriors </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and prepare for battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3352970/extras/28ad32ade2bdc1cca734bd1b334030af.avif?t=1738853871\" width=367 height=79 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Anima, the enigmatic Dungeon Mistress, rules with cunning and power. In her dark domain, six slaves fight under her command, facing brutal and challenging trials. However, the battles are not only physical; Anima designs these confrontations to forge indomitable warriors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3352970/extras/6aa98c3b917d6d2da2654af63d5cfddd.avif?t=1738853871\" width=367 height=79 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Currently, the game includes:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 7 playable characters</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 6 stages</p><p class=\"bb_para